data.name: ChangeLogTextBox.Text
data.value:
TextPad+ 2.9.0
Main changes: —Added autosave —Added the ability to save all files —The search window has been moved to the panel below —Added the ability to select encoding in the "File" menu —Added the ability to open links in the browser and turn off their backlighting
Corrections: —Fixed a bug due to which the color scheme did not change —Minor bug fixes — Improved update system —Tab stops shortened to 4 spaces —Improved logging system —Fixed a bug with marking unsaved files when changing the theme —Fix minor bugs
